Ex-WWE Diva Kelly Kelly's Still Ring Ready with Insane Bikini Bod Ex WWE Diva Kelly Kelly Still Ring-Ready With Insane Bikini Bod 2/27/2017 4:01 PM PST 
Kelly Kelly 's body is still fit for a few rounds ... with her husband on South Beach. 
The ex-WWE Diva flaunted her sick bod while packing on the PDA with her husband, retired NHL star, Sheldon Souray . 
It's been 4 years since she stepped in the squared circle, but she can still drop a figure four necklock on us! Not that she's offering.
